{"tid":331419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【專家𢱑頭】新癌藥令病人白髮變黑 對健康人士卻有嚴重副作用","createTime":"2017-07-22T07:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T09:20:07.000Z","uid":47272,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ddb441debadd351c3e770a35e21badd51ff6a1","tid":331419,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"【專家𢱑頭】新癌藥令病人白髮變黑 對健康人士卻有嚴重副作用<br />\n不少癌症病人都會因化療或服抗癌藥導致脫髮，然而有研究意外發現，有服用3款新抗癌藥的病人竟然白髮變黑，不過專家強調，新癌藥對健康人士有嚴重副作用，不能直接用為黑髮藥。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙的專家跟進研究52名肺癌病人，服用3款免疫療法新藥「Keytruda」、「Opdivo」及「Tecentriq」後會否出現不良副作用，意外發現當中14位、部份是年滿70歲的病人，原本的白髮在服藥後慢慢變成黑或深啡色。有13名病人是一頭白髮完全變色，另外一人就是局部變黑。<br />\n<br />\n專家同時發現，這14位髮色有改變的病人，當中只有一位病情沒有改善，所以他們相信髮色改變或是新藥起作用的證明。<br />\n<br />\n有份參與研究的巴塞隆拿自治大學（Autonomous University of Barcelona）皮膚科專家里韋拉（Noelia Rivera）稱，最初以為「白髮變黑」只是個別例子，想不到還有其他服藥病人也出現同樣情況。但奇怪的是，早前有研究指，同款藥物或令有黑色素瘤的病人頭髮變白，今次發現令專家十分困惑。<br />\n<br />\n美國西北大學（Northwestern University）皮膚科專家魯賓遜（June Robinson）表示這次結果值得深入研究，但強調要將新抗癌藥當成「白髮救星」是言之尚早。里韋拉亦表示，要做更多研究確認結果，並指出新抗癌藥會對身體健康的人造成嚴重副作用，不過一旦確認新藥能夠影響髮色，或可以此研發出另一款改善白髮的藥物。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6p9xskz0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6p9xskz0&h=c3adcf7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/msfz165x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmsfz165x&h=7b4c67f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170722&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56987653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170722%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56987653&d=b9yxPpJKNKz6P7TRKkHualzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=c86141ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170722%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56987653&h=134aedf0\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170722&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56987653</a>"},{"pid":"c9376f05f02c1cd5cd6feb00c57762d2fa7e0024","tid":331419,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T07:23:21.000Z","msg":"咁似美容廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a626e598669c6b784220ad3a2a50fabe833eb7a2","tid":331419,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"可能係免疫細胞某類機制，控制黑色素細胞生長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b7cf80299afa24c18c631939e6c0c52d0e35d7","tid":331419,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"k"},{"pid":"dea9f04009c6ecfed8eefe2541c99788fba7022a","tid":331419,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"要靚唔要命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f995ff77043a89c25dd94841419137feeb32401","tid":331419,"uid":37502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:07:59.000Z","msg":"負負得正？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5345f965e5ceec92b173499083113f55373d749d","tid":331419,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"自古以來 科學有唔少成就都係意外發現出來<br />\n得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}